OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy overnight with the
OL,7,Fchance of showers, along with a few
OL,8,Foccasional clearer spells towards the
OL,9,Feast of the region. Breezy with
OL,10,Ftemperatures relatively mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with showers,
OL,13,Fthese will likely ease during the
OL,14,Fafternoon with some sunny spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping. Clear periods overnight
OL,16,Fmay allow for a patchy frost to
OL,17,Fdevelop.
